Package com.vasilitate.vapp.sdk.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidApplicationVappIdException
    An exception that is thrown when an attempt is made to set the SDK's application Vapp Id to an invalid format.
    InvalidProductIdException
    An exception that is thrown when an attempt is made to create an invalid Product.
    InvalidSimException
    An exception that is thrown when the device's does not have a SIM in a ready state.
    InvalidSmsCountException
    An exception that is thrown when an SMS count for a product exceeds the allowed bounds by the SDK
    InvalidVappNetworkException
    An exception that is thrown when the SMS network is not valid
    InvalidVappNumberException
    An exception that is thrown when the Vapp number range is incorrect
    InvalidVappProductException
    An exception that is thrown when a product's configuration is invalid
    InvalidVappProgressException
    An exception that is thrown when an attempt is made to set an invalid progress for a product
    NetworkNotSupportedException
    An exception that is thrown when the device is not connected to an originating network
    VappException
    A general exception which is thrown by the VAPP! SDK
